trans-unit.source: Contains a global default proxy instance for all HTTP requests.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en global proxy Standardforekomst for HTTP-forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: The GlobalProxySelection stores the proxy settings for the default proxy that <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> instances use to contact Internet sites beyond the local network.
trans-unit.target: GlobalProxySelection lagrer proxy-innstillinger for standard proxy som <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>forekomster bruke til å kontakte Internett-områder utenfor det lokale nettverket.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The default proxy setting is initialized from the global or application configuration file, and can be overridden for individual requests or disabled by setting the <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest.Proxy%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to the result of the <xref:System.Net.GlobalProxySelection.GetEmptyWebProxy%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Standard proxy-innstillingen er initialisert fra globale eller programmet konfigurasjonsfilen, og kan overstyres for individuelle forespørsler eller deaktiveres ved å angi den <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest.Proxy%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen resultatet av den <xref:System.Net.GlobalProxySelection.GetEmptyWebProxy%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Net.GlobalProxySelection.GetEmptyWebProxy%2A> </xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest.Proxy%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The proxy settings stored in GlobalProxySelection are used by any <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> derived objects that support proxies and have their <xref:System.Net.WebRequest.Proxy%2A> property value set to `null` (the default).
trans-unit.target: Proxyinnstillinger som er lagret i GlobalProxySelection brukes av en <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>avledet objekter som støtter proxyer og har de <xref:System.Net.WebRequest.Proxy%2A>egenskapsverdien satt til `null` (standard).</xref:System.Net.WebRequest.Proxy%2A> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: Proxies are currently supported by <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>, <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>, and <xref:System.Net.WebClient>.
trans-unit.target: Proxy-servere støttes for øyeblikket av <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>, <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>, og <xref:System.Net.WebClient>.</xref:System.Net.WebClient> </xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest> </xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: **Note** Changes to the GlobalProxySelection after a request is made are not reflected in a <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>.
trans-unit.target: **Obs** endringer i GlobalProxySelection når en forespørsel ikke skal vises i en <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Net.GlobalProxySelection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Net.GlobalProxySelection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The GetEmptyWebProxy method returns a blank <xref:System.Net.IWebProxy> instance to indicate that no proxy is used to access an Internet resource.
trans-unit.target: GetEmptyWebProxy returneres en tom <xref:System.Net.IWebProxy>forekomsten til å angi at ingen proxy brukes til å få tilgang til en Internett-ressurs.</xref:System.Net.IWebProxy>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the global HTTP proxy.

The Select property sets the proxy that all <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> instances use if the request supports proxies and no proxy is set explicitly using the <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest.Proxy%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Velg egenskapen angir proxyen alle <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>forekomster bruke hvis forespørselen støtter proxyer og ingen proxy angis eksplisitt ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest.Proxy%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest.Proxy%2A> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: Proxies are currently supported by <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest> and <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>.
An <xref:System.Net.IWebProxy> that every call to <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A?displayProperty=fullName> uses.
The value specified for a set operation was <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som er angitt for en set-operasjon ble <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Oppkalleren har ikke tillatelse for den forespurte operasjonen.
